Subject: [PATCH 25/44] sysrepo upstream API change: NULL output on RPCs
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Organization: Wires

Depends-on: https://gerrit.cesnet.cz/c/CzechLight/dependencies/+/8289
